gutom ka ba? nauuhaw? Ano ang kailangan mo?

171
00:15:17,368 --> 00:15:19,495
- Nars! Nars...
- Okay.

172
00:15:19,704 --> 00:15:21,331
Lorelei, okay lang ako.

173
00:15:22,165 --> 00:15:23,165
Okay.

174
00:15:26,210 --> 00:15:27,378
Nahihilo ka ba?

175
00:15:31,758 --> 00:15:33,134
Huwag i-stress ang iyong sarili.

176
00:15:36,387 --> 00:15:37,388
Dahan-dahan.

177
00:15:41,225 --> 00:15:42,225
Teka.

178
00:15:42,769 --> 00:15:44,062
Paano ako nakarating dito?

179
00:15:46,189 --> 00:15:49,484
Huwag mong sabihin sa akin
Dinala mo ba ako dito sa campus?

180
00:15:50,485 --> 00:15:53,613
Baka ako mismo ang nagdala sayo
kung hindi ako nakakuha ng tulong.

181
00:15:54,697 --> 00:15:56,532
Loki, gising na!

182
00:15:56,824 --> 00:15:59,452
Tulong. Tulong!

183
00:16:00,954 --> 00:16:02,246
Tulong!

184
00:16:03,665 --> 00:16:05,583
- Walang malay si Loki.
- Loki!

185
00:16:06,209 --> 00:16:08,044
Loki! Loki!

186
00:16:10,463 --> 00:16:11,631
Tulong!

187
00:16:12,298 --> 00:16:13,675
Kumuha ng tulong dito!

188
00:16:14,592 --> 00:16:15,592
Tulong.

189
00:16:20,974 --> 00:16:25,061
Buti na lang Professor Morayta
ay malapit sa clubroom

190
00:16:25,353 --> 00:16:27,605
at agad na humingi ng tulong,

191
00:16:27,939 --> 00:16:30,233
para dalhin ka dito sa ospital.

192
00:16:33,069 --> 00:16:35,321
