206
00:17:21,826 --> 00:17:24,620
Kaya kailangan mong magpahinga ng marami, okay?

207
00:17:25,413 --> 00:17:27,582
Nakuha ko. salamat po.

208
00:17:30,752 --> 00:17:34,589
Nga pala, anong nangyari
sa kainuman ko?

209
00:17:35,131 --> 00:17:36,382
